profile:
The Sunburst Advantage is Our Dedication

At Sunburst Shutters & Closets, we offer products, services, and philosophies that make us a leader in the home design industry. As we continue to deliver exceptional services, we are proud to announce that we have partnered with  Sonata Design, a leader in the industry of window fashions, home automation and interior finishes. 

With our signature Polywood shutters and a vast selection of closet collections, paired with Sonata's patented Symphony collection, we bring life to homes with a design that looks toward longevity, performance, and aesthetics. 

Sunburst Shutters & Closets and Sonata Design provides the full breadth of home design options to help you achieve your vision

profile: Since 1992, Competition Window Coverings has been providing the lower mainland with the best available window coverings products on the market. Our objective is, and always has been to deliver both nationally recognized brand name products as well as locally manufactured products at the best possible price without sacrificing the quality of the product. We have searched the market for the best value for your window covering dollar and found a large selection of products in many price ranges, Our friendly sales staff and their many years of experience within the industry help ensure you get the right look for your home or office. All our products are custom made (ensuring the proper fit), manufactured with the highest quality materials and come with a quick delivery time as well as service that’s second to none.
